parameters: Red Man: Ah, ah, ah, let me say it first.

Red Man: I am Red Mutant, a mechanical engineer,
and a high-ranking member of the organization.

Red: If you cross that line, I will consider it as
hostility.
Red: Okay?

\C[18]Sakura\C[0]: Oh, so even a mere mutant criminal dares
to say that?

\C[23]Rurika\C[0]: Unfortunately, our mission is to defeat
evil like you.

Sakura & Rurika: Let's do it, Kenichi. We'll do
it, Mr. Kenichi.
\C[11]Kenichi\C[0]: ...U-understood!!
